metadata.title: Senate Session starts,set to resume debate on Finance Bill 2025-26

content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Jun 17 (APP):The budget session of the Upper House of Parliament commenced at 11:05 am Tuesday, with Senate Chairman Syed Yousaf Raza Gilani presiding over the proceedings. Senators will continue their deliberations on the Finance Bill 2025-26 during the session, examining its key provisions and potential impact.
